---
import TextBubble from '../components/about/TextBubble.astro';
import TextBubbleWrap from '../components/about/TextBubbleWrap.astro';
import Icon from '../components/Icon.astro';
import SectionHeaderTitle from '../components/SectionHeaderTitle.astro';
import Square from '../components/Square.astro';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionLayout from '../layouts/SectionLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Mosaiq Software">
    <SectionLayout id="join">
        <SectionHeaderTitle>Join</SectionHeaderTitle>
        <Square
            width={10}
            size={'20vw'}
            color="var(--mosaiq-navy)"
            top="400px"
            right="10%"
            rotation="10deg"
        />
        <Square
            width={10}
            size={'45vw'}
            color="var(--mosaiq-magenta)"
            top="500px"
            left="20%"
            rotation="40deg"
        />
        <Square
            width={10}
            size={'25vw'}
            color="var(--mosaiq-blue)"
            top="-50px"
            left="50%"
            rotation="20deg"
        />
        <TextBubbleWrap>
            <TextBubble amount="10%">
                <h2>Do you find yourself chronically building something?<br />So do we.</h2>
                <p>Whether you&rsquo;re hunting for your next big project or just want something fun to tinker with on weekends, Mosaiq has a spot for you. We welcome coders, designers, dreamers, and anyone who loves to create.</p>
            </TextBubble>
            <TextBubble amount="25%">
                <h4>What we look for</h4>
                <p class="subheading">Required</p>
                <p>&bull; 18+ years of life experience</p>
                <p>&bull; A brain full of ideas (good, bad, or gloriously weird)</p>
                <p>&bull; Curiosity and a hunger to learn new skills</p>
                <p>&bull; The itch to build things just because you can</p>
            </TextBubble>
            <TextBubble amount="30%">
                <p class="subheading">Nice to have</p>
                <p>&bull; Any web dev experience (HTML, CSS, JavaScript, TypeScript, React, etc.)</p>
                <p>&bull; Any experience with software or game development</p>
                <p>&bull; An eye for design, graphics, or UX</p>
            </TextBubble>
            <TextBubble amount="20%">
                <p class="subheading">Why join?</p>
                <p>Because you&rsquo;ll get real project experience: the kind you can put on a resume, brag about in interviews, or just show off to your friends. No grades. No payroll. Just the joy of building something awesome and the skills you&rsquo;ll pick up along the way.</p>
            </TextBubble>
            <TextBubble amount="35%">
                <h4>How to join</h4>
                <p>
                    Skip the fancy applications. Just shoot us an email at <a
                        href="mailto:join@mosaiq.dev"
                        target="_blank"
                        >join@mosaiq.dev</a
                    > with your resume or portfolio and a quick hello. That&rsquo;s it!
                </p>
            </TextBubble>
        </TextBubbleWrap>
        <TextBubbleWrap>
            <TextBubble amount="20%">
                <div class="spread">
                    <div class="spread-icon">
                        <Icon name={'chevron-down'} />
                    </div>
                    <h3>Smallprint</h3>
                </div>
            </TextBubble>
            <div class="smallprint">
                <TextBubble amount="20%">
                    <p>Mosaiq is a nonprofit, member-run organization. This is not a full-time job or a paid position. Instead, it&rsquo;s a side commitment where you can gain real project experience, collaborate with others, and build meaningful software.</p>
                </TextBubble>
                <TextBubble amount="20%">
                    <p class="subheading">A few important notes:</p>
                    <p>&bull; There is no compensation. Any revenue Mosaiq generates is fully reinvested into operations or directed toward charitable initiatives such as scholarships.</p>
                    <p>&bull; While this is a part-time, flexible opportunity, members are expected to balance Mosaiq with classes, work, and other obligations.</p>
                    <p>&bull; We cannot sponsor work visas or provide employment authorization at this time.</p>
                </TextBubble>
                <TextBubble amount="20%">
                    <p class="subheading">What we&rsquo;re really looking for in candidates:</p>
                    <p>&bull; A genuine interest in building, learning, and experimenting with software.</p>
                    <p>&bull; Reliability. People who follow through and contribute consistently.</p>
                    <p>&bull; Collaboration skills. An openness to feedback, willingness to help teammates, and a drive to build together.</p>
                    <p>&bull; Creativity and curiosity. Whether you&rsquo;re coding, designing, or brainstorming, we want members who bring energy and ideas.</p>
                </TextBubble>
                <TextBubble amount="20%">
                    <p>In short: if you&rsquo;re looking for a paycheck, Mosaiq isn&rsquo;t for you. If you&rsquo;re looking for experience, community, and the chance to make a real impact through code, you&rsquo;ll fit right in.</p>
                </TextBubble>
            </div>
        </TextBubbleWrap>
    </SectionLayout>
</BaseLayout>
<script>
    import { gsap } from 'gsap';

    document.querySelector('.spread')!.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const smallprints = document.querySelectorAll('.smallprint');
        smallprints.forEach((el) => {
            if (el.classList.contains('expanded')) {
                gsap.to(el, { height: 0, duration: 0.5, ease: 'power2.inOut' });
                el.classList.remove('expanded');
            } else {
                const fullHeight = el.scrollHeight;
                gsap.to(el, { height: fullHeight, duration: 0.5, ease: 'power2.inOut' });
                el.classList.add('expanded');
            }
        });
        gsap.to('.spread-icon', { rotate: smallprints[0].classList.contains('expanded') ? 180 : 0, duration: 0.5, ease: 'power2.inOut' });
    });
</script>
<style>
    p {
        font-size: var(--font-size-md);
        max-width: 80ch;
    }

    .subheading {
        color: var(--color-text-secondary);
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    }

    a {
        color: var(--mosaiq-magenta);
    }

    .spread {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .smallprint {
        overflow: hidden;
        width: 100%;
        height: 0;
    }
</style>
